<div id="privacy" class="content-section active">
    <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>
        <strong>Effective Date:</strong> April 7, 2026<br>
        <strong>Last Updated:</strong> April 7, 2026
    </p>

    <h3>1. Introduction</h3>
    <p>
        LogisticLink is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect,
        use, store, and protect your information when you use the LogisticLink mobile application ("App") —
        an AI-powered logistics and transportation platform that connects users with drivers and transport
        providers for delivery, relocation, and cargo movement services.
    </p>
    <p>By using LogisticLink, you consent to this Privacy Policy.</p>

    <h3>2. Information We Collect</h3>

    <h4>2.1 Information You Provide</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Full name</li>
        <li>Phone number</li>
        <li>Email address (optional)</li>
        <li>Profile photo</li>
        <li>Pickup and delivery locations</li>
        <li>Item images uploaded for AI analysis</li>
        <li>Delivery instructions and notes</li>
        <li>Payment details (mobile money or card transactions)</li>
        <li>Support messages and feedback</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>2.2 Automatically Collected Information</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Device information (model, OS version)</li>
        <li>IP address and approximate location</li>
        <li>App usage data</li>
        <li>GPS location (for tracking deliveries)</li>
        <li>Crash logs and performance data</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>2.3 Logistics Data</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Shipment details (pickup, destination, route)</li>
        <li>Vehicle selection and delivery preferences</li>
        <li>Driver interaction and tracking data</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>2.4 Optional Information</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Location permissions for real-time tracking</li>
        <li>Biometric login (stored only on device)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>3. How We Use Your Information</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>To create and manage your account</li>
        <li>To process delivery and logistics requests</li>
        <li>To connect you with drivers and transport providers</li>
        <li>To enable AI item detection and cargo estimation</li>
        <li>To provide real-time delivery tracking</li>
        <li>To process payments</li>
        <li>To improve app performance and features</li>
        <li>To detect fraud and ensure security</li>
        <li>To provide customer support</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="highlight-box">
        We do <strong>NOT</strong> sell your personal data to third parties.
    </div>

    <h3>4. Sharing of Information</h3>
    <p>We may share your information with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Drivers and transport providers</strong> — to fulfill delivery requests</li>
        <li><strong>Payment providers</strong> — for processing transactions</li>
        <li><strong>Cloud and analytics services</strong></li>
        <li><strong>Legal authorities</strong> — where required by law</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>5. Data Storage & Retention</h3>
    <p>
        Your data is stored securely using encryption and industry-standard protections.
        We retain necessary records for operational, legal, and security purposes.
    </p>

    <h3>6. Your Rights</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Access your data</strong></li>
        <li><strong>Correct your data</strong></li>
        <li><strong>Delete your account</strong></li>
        <li><strong>Withdraw consent</strong></li>
    </ul>

    <p>Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@logisticlink.com">support@logisticlink.com</a></p>

    <h3>7. Children's Privacy</h3>
    <p>LogisticLink is intended for users aged 18 and above.</p>

    <h3>8. Changes</h3>
    <p>We may update this policy and notify users via the app.</p>

    <h3>9. Contact</h3>
    <p>📧 support@logisticlink.com</p>
    <p>📍 Tanzania</p>
